searchKeywords":["and","those","that","died","the","plague","were","four","twenty","thousand"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_25_10","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":25,"verse":10,"text":"And the Lord spoke to Moses, saying,","searchKeywords":["and","the","lord","spoke","moses","saying"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_25_11","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":25,"verse":11,"text":"Phinees the son of Eleazar the son of Aaron the priest has caused my wrath to cease from the children of Israel, when I was exceedingly jealous among them, and I did not consume the children of Israel in my jealousy.","searchKeywords":["phinees","the","son","eleazar","aaron","priest","has","caused","wrath","cease","from","children","israel","when","was","exceedingly","jealous","among","them","and","did","not","consume","jealousy"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_25_12","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":25,"verse":12,"text":"Thus do thou say , Behold, I give him a covenant of peace:","searchKeywords":["thus","thou","say","behold","give","him","covenant","peace"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_25_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":25,"verse":13,"text":"and he and his seed after him shall have a perpetual covenant of priesthood, because he was zealous for his God, and made atonement for the children of Israel.","searchKeywords":["and","his","seed","after","him","shall","have","perpetual","covenant","priesthood","because","was","zealous","for","god","made","atonement","the","children","israel"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_25_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":25,"verse":14,"text":"Now the name of the smitten Israeliti